317
00:16:32,140 --> 00:16:34,010
When I was little,
I also had a princess dream.

318
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:36,640
It's perfectly normal for girls.

319
00:16:38,890 --> 00:16:40,260
So, you don't need to feel guilty.

320
00:16:41,930 --> 00:16:43,510
Just tell me the truth.

321
00:16:43,510 --> 00:16:44,850
Do you like the Zhu family?

322
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:49,510
At first, I did like it.

323
00:16:50,180 --> 00:16:51,180
But that's because

324
00:16:51,640 --> 00:16:53,550
