325
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:57,300
Then what do you think

326
00:16:57,300 --> 00:16:58,400
about Mr. Zhu's suggestion?

327
00:16:59,140 --> 00:17:00,010
Jing'an,

328
00:17:00,180 --> 00:17:02,180
