375
00:19:31,850 --> 00:19:32,720
Dad, Mom.

376
00:19:32,980 --> 00:19:34,260
I'm leaving.

377
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:37,140
Don't worry.

378
00:19:37,140 --> 00:19:38,430
